      "text": "The dream of turning Sapphire Isle into a land of joy has fractured. Lorelei bid her final farewell to this world, leaving behind nothing but a tainted name and a broken Siren's Tear. In the Sage's office, her personal belongings had been completely cleared away. I saw how she had spent a fortune in the auction house, we exchanged thoughts about the Mistbound Terror, and we hatched our last plan together. Yet that brilliant woman vanished without a trace, as if she too had been nothing more than an illusion woven by the devices on Sapphire Isle.",
